  "code": "%%{Education_GradeSync}}}%%\nsequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    participant R as 🖼️ Renderer<br/>(Education_ClassroomService)\n    participant P as 📡 Preload<br/>(Education_ContentCDN)\n    participant M as 🖥️ Main<br/>(Education_GradeSync)\n    participant S as ⚙️ Services\n    participant MCP as 🤖 MCP Servers\n    participant LM as 🧠 LM Studio\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Application Initialization\n    \n    R->>P: DOMContentLoaded\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke(Education_GradeSync)\n    M-->>P: {Education_ContentCDN}\n    P-->>R: version\n    \n    R->>P: Initialize LM Studio\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke(Education_ContentCDN)\n    M->>S: lmStudioClient.connect(Education_LMS_Portal)\n    S->>LM: HTTP GET /v1/models\n    LM-->>S: {Education_ContentCDN] }\n    S-->>M: {Education_ClassroomService}\n    M-->>P: status\n    P-->>R: Update UI\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Chat Message Flow\n    \n    R->>P: User sends chat message\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke(Education_ContentCDN)\n    M->>S: chatbotService.processMessage(Education_ContentCDN)\n    \n    alt Intent: Knowledge Query\n        S->>MCP: evony_search(Education_LMS_Portal)\n        MCP-->>S: {Education_ContentCDN] }\n    else Intent: Calculation\n        S->>MCP: calc_training(Education_LMS_Portal)\n        MCP-->>S: {Education_ClassroomService} }\n    else Intent: Protocol\n        S->>MCP: protocol_lookup(Education_ContentCDN)\n        MCP-->>S: {Education_GradeSync} }\n    end\n    \n    S->>S: Build context from MCP results\n    S->>LM: POST /v1/chat/completions\n    LM-->>S: {Education_LMS_Portal}\n    S-->>M: formatted response\n    M-->>P: response\n    P-->>R: Display in chat\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Traffic Capture Flow\n    \n    R->>P: Webview traffic detected\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.send(Education_ClassroomService)\n    M->>S: proxyMonitor.processPacket(Education_StudentDB)\n    S->>S: Decode AMF3\n    S->>S: Identify action\n    S->>S: Update game state\n    M->>P: mainWindow.webContents.send(Education_StudentDB)\n    P->>R: Update traffic list\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Settings Flow\n    \n    R->>P: User saves settings\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke(Education_GradeSync)\n    M->>S: store.set(Education_StudentDB)\n    M->>S: lmStudioClient.updateSettings(Education_ClassroomService)\n    S->>LM: Reconnect if URL changed\n    M-->>P: {Education_LMS_Portal}\n    P-->>R: Show confirmation\n",
